; --- Notes ---
; Balanced preset rationale:
; - Moderate base lot with fixed sizing and per-trade risk ~2% of account when dynamic sizing is enabled.
; - No martingale to avoid escalating drawdowns; instead rely on trend + volatility filters.
; - EMA (50) trend filter + MACD + ATR + optional MA crossover and Bollinger breakout increase signal quality.
; - Wider SL (80 points) with multiple TP levels to let trends develop and capture larger moves.
; - Trailing stop (ATR-based) and breakeven protect profits once trades move in favor.
; - Partial close at TP1 to lock profits and reduce exposure on extended moves.
; - News and time filters enabled to avoid volatile, low-liquidity periods.
; - Test extensively across multiple symbols/timeframes and adjust LotSize / RiskPercent to match your account and comfort with drawdowns.
